paragraphs.text: %sql select glatitude as lat, glongitude as lon, cast (sum(case when length(gtavg) = 0 then 0.0 else cast(gtavg as double) end)/sum(case when length(gtavg) = 0 then 0 else 1 end) as decimal(10,2)) as tavg from gmos_parquet where year = '2000' and season = 'winter' and length(gtavg) != 0 group by glatitude, glongitude

%sql select year, cast (sum(case when length(gtavg) = 0 then 0.0 else cast(gtavg as double) end)/sum(case when length(gtavg) = 0 then 0 else 1 end) as decimal(10,2)) as tavg from gmos_parquet where length(gtavg) != 0 group by year order by year

%sql select year, season, cast (sum(case when length(gtavg) = 0 then 0.0 else cast(gtavg as double) end)/sum(case when length(gtavg) = 0 then 0 else 1 end) as decimal(10,2)) as tavg from gmos_parquet where length(gtavg) != 0 group by year, season order by year, season

val gson = new com.google.gson.Gson()
val bubbles = sqlContext.sql(s"""select glatitude as lat, glongitude as lon, cast (sum(case when length(gtavg) = 0 then 0.0 else cast(gtavg as double) end)/sum(case when length(gtavg) = 0 then 0 else 1 end) as decimal(10,2)) as tavg from gmos_parquet where year = '2000' and season = 'winter' and length(gtavg) != 0 group by glatitude, glongitude""").map{r=>
Map(
"radius" -> Math.round(Math.abs(Option(r(2)).getOrElse("0").toString.toDouble)/5.0+0.5),
"tavg" -> r(2),
"latitude" -> r(0),
"longitude" -> r(1),
"fillKey" -> Math.abs(Math.round(Option(r(2)).getOrElse("0").toString.toDouble))%20
)
}.collect.map(s=>scala.collection.JavaConversions.mapAsJavaMap(s))
val bubblesJson = gson.toJson(bubbles)
